### ============================================================
### 길드 다이렉트 메시지 (DM) APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### DM 대화 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/dm/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 특정 사용자와의 대화 시작/조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/dm/conversations/other-user-id
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### DM 전송
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/dm/send/recipient-user-id
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello! Nice to meet you."
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 대화 ID로 메시지 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/dm/conversations/1/messages?page=0&size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 상대방 ID로 메시지 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/dm/messages/other-user-id?page=0&size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 이전 메시지 조회 (무한 스크롤)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/dm/conversations/1/messages/before/100?page=0&size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 메시지 읽음 처리
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/dm/conversations/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 전체 안읽은 DM 수 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/dm/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 메시지 삭제
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/guilds/1/dm/messages/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
